          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1599559902347-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash the <strong>spinach </strong>then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Once everything is cooked, add the <strong>spinach</strong> and then cook, covered for a further 1-2 min or until wilted</p><p>Give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>Indonesian-style chicken & mushroom rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1599559911615-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1599559911615-x400.jpg",
