            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1599559911615-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Indonesian-style chicken & mushroom rice</strong> and drizzle over with the <strong>satay sauce</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>spring onion greens</strong>, <strong>chopped chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and the <strong>lime wedges</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
